*中華民國－諾魯主要進口項目：纖維素紙漿、紙或紙板之製造或整理之機械、首飾及其配件等。<ref name=bft>{{Cite web|url = https://www.trade.gov.tw/World/Detail.aspx?nodeID=45&pid=581418|title = 各國經貿資訊|publisher = [[經濟部國際貿易局|經濟部國際貿易局]]|date = 2018-02-08|accessdate = 2018-03-04|archive-date = 2018-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180304231414/https://www.trade.gov.tw/World/Detail.aspx?nodeID=45&pid=581418|dead-url = no}}</ref>

